Mala Ebû Habîb, mala Ebû Habîb.
 
The house of Abu Habib, the house of Abu Habib.

505
00:37:04,000 --> 00:37:05,000
Ebû Habîb.
 
Abu Habib.

506
00:37:05,000 --> 00:37:06,000
Ser çava.
 
Upon my eyes (You're welcome).

507
