547
00:38:37,000 --> 00:38:39,000
Na, berê de xwendine.
 
No, from the past they study.

548
00:38:39,000 --> 00:38:40,000
Ji berê de.
 
From the past.

549
00:38:40,000 --> 00:38:41,000
Erê.
 
Yes.

550
00:38:41,000 --> 00:38:47,000
Wextê me berê de xwendin e, me xwend... me camî'eyan birne
