551
00:38:47,000 --> 00:38:50,000
Am... tiştinê xirab in de nakim am mal in.
 
We... don't do bad things, we are at home.

552
00:38:50,000 --> 00:38:54,000
Gund, wan bi hev ra... jinên gundê Kurzelê... çawa ne? Bi
