569
00:39:27,000 --> 00:39:28,000
Basûtê!
 
Basûtê!

570
00:39:28,000 --> 00:39:31,000
Êh... cîranên ev in ne...
 
Eh... these are neighbors...

571
00:39:31,000 --> 00:39:33,000
